                            <comment id="16387127" author="caomanhdat" created="Tue, 6 Mar 2018 01:42:01 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I think by increasing the timeout to 10 seconds will be enough. According to&#160;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-11443&quot; title=&quot;Remove the usage of workqueue for Overseer&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;SOLR-11443&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;SOLR-11443&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, within 10 seconds around 30000 messages can be processed which is more than enough for creating a collection with 1024 shards and 3 replicas each.&#160;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
